title: Early Doors (2003 - 2004) Complete Series 1 + 2
description:
Early Doors complete series 1 and 2 (2003 - 2004)


Gentle paced comedy series set in a small public house (The Grapes)in Stockport, Greater Manchester. Landlord Ken has been left by his wife (for his best friend), but lives with his adopted daughter Melanie and mother Jean. He is assisted at the bar by reliable Tanya.

The regulars in the pub include lazy skiving husbands Joe and Duffy; dense but friendly couple Eddie and Joan; old git Tommy; and useless coppers Phil and Nige.


Writers: Craig Cash, Phil Mealey

Starring: John Henshaw, Craig Cash, Phil Mealey, Rita May, Christine Bottomley, Rodney Litchfield, Mark Benton, Lorraine Cheshire, James Quinn, Peter Wight, Susan Cookson

Series 1: 6 episodes Broadcast 2003 BBC Two
Series 2: 6 episodes Broadcast 2004 BBC Two

12 x 30 min episodes
